                                                                                                                                   Karanjia

              
	Mumbai, Feb. 1 (PTI): R.K. Karanjia, veteran journalist and former editor of Blitz, died at his home today. He was 95.
    
	He is survived by daughter Rita Mehta, the editor of Cine Blitz. 
    
	Condoling his death, Prime Minister Manmohan Singh said Karanjia had set many new landmarks in journalism.
                                                                                
